# Active Directory Enterprise Lab

## Objective

Build a Windows Server 2022 Active Directory environment to simulate an enterprise network and develop hands-on experience with Windows infrastructure, authentication, DNS, DHCP, and Group Policy.

---

## Technologies

- Windows Server 2022
- Windows 11
- Active Directory Domain Services
- DNS
- DHCP
- Group Policy
- PowerShell
- Oracle VM VirtualBox

---

## Lab Environment

- Domain Controller: DC01
- Client: Windows 11
- Domain: corp.local
- Static IP addressing
- Internal virtual network

---

## Skills Demonstrated

- Installed Active Directory Domain Services
- Promoted a Windows Server to a Domain Controller
- Configured DNS
- Configured DHCP
- Joined Windows 11 client to the domain
- Created users and Organizational Units (OUs)
- Applied Group Policy Objects (GPOs)
- Used PowerShell for administration and troubleshooting
- Validated network connectivity

---

